                     <interp inst="t18310106-148-person1324" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in th same house - this girl called out; I ran down stairs and took the prisoner, who had just got to the door with the trunk.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310106-148-person1325">
                  THOMAS 
                  DELANY
